&#39;\b&#39; is a _word boundary_, &#39;|&#39; is _OR_, &#39;(?i)&#39; — _ignore case_ flag. All list of patterns you can find [here](http://docs.oracle.com/javase/7/docs/api/java/util/regex/Pattern.html) and probably you should learn about regex.

